text: Dario Vidošević was a rowing coxswain from Yugoslavia. Vidošević competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics. He was born on 13 April 1968 and died on 27 May 2020.Dario Vidošević == References == Category:1968 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Rowers Category:Olympians for Yugoslavia Category:Sportspeople from Split
